s=\"32x32\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon-16x16.png\" sizes=\"16x16\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"\n          geist_9e050971-module__05dp7a__className\n          bg-[#F7F6F3]\n          text-neutral-900\n          antialiased\n        \"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><header class=\"   sticky   top-0   z-50   border-b   border-neutral-200/60   bg-[#F7F6F3]/90   backdrop-blur-md   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   flex   max-w-[1280px]   items-center   justify-between   px-6   py-5   \"><a class=\"   text-xl   font-light   tracking-[0.25em]   uppercase   text-neutral-900   \" href=\"/\">tinysorted</a><nav class=\"   hidden   md:flex   items-center   gap-8   text-sm   text-neutral-600   \"><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/minimalist-living\">Minimalist Living</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/kitchen\">kitchen</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a></nav><a aria-label=\"Search\" class=\"   flex   items-center   justify-center   w-10   h-10   rounded-full   border   border-neutral-200   hover:bg-white   transition   \" href=\"/search\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></a></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><!--$--><main class=\"bg-[#F7F6F3] min-h-screen\"><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-[900px] px-6 py-20\"><p class=\"   mb-4   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.25em]   text-neutral-500   \">Contributors</p><h1 class=\"   text-5xl   md:text-7xl   font-light   tracking-[-0.03em]   text-neutral-900   \">Write For Us</h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-neutral-500\">Last updated: June 2026</p><div class=\"   mt-14   space-y-10   text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Become a TinySorted Contributor</h2><p>TinySorted welcomes experienced writers, home organization enthusiasts, interior designers, productivity experts, and minimalist lifestyle advocates who are passionate about helping people create better living spaces.</p><p class=\"mt-4\">We publish practical, well-researched, evergreen content that helps readers organize their homes, maximize small spaces, and live more intentionally.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Topics We Accept</h2><ul class=\"list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Home organization</li><li>Small-space living</li><li>Storage ideas</li><li>Kitchen organization</li><li>Minimalist lifestyle</li><li>Apartment living</li><li>Decluttering guides</li><li>Productivity at home</li><li>Furniture recommendations</li><li>Storage product reviews</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Editorial Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"list-disc space-y-3 pl-6\"><li>Original content only.</li><li>No AI-generated spam or rewritten articles.</li><li>Minimum 1,200 words.</li><li>Well structured using headings.</li><li>Factually accurate and properly researched.</li><li>Written in clear, natural English.</li><li>No excessive promotional language.</li><li>Include practical examples whenever possible.</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">What We Don&#x27;t Accept</h2><ul class=\"list-disc space-y-3 pl-6\"><li>Duplicate content.</li><li>Plagiarized material.</li><li>Articles written solely for backlinks.</li><li>Casino, cryptocurrency, gambling, or adult content.</li><li>Purely promotional articles.</li><li>Keyword stuffing.</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Submission Process</h2><ol class=\"list-decimal space-y-3 pl-6\"><li>Send us your topic idea or completed article.</li><li>Our editorial team reviews every submission.</li><li>We may suggest revisions before publication.</li><li>Approved articles are scheduled for publication.</li></ol></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Author Benefits</h2><ul class=\"list-disc space-y-3 pl-6\"><li>Author profile on TinySorted.</li><li>Professional writing portfolio.</li><li>Exposure to a growing audience.</li><li>Opportunity for future collaborations.</li></ul></section><section class=\"rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-light text-neutral-900\">Ready to Pitch?</h2><p class=\"mt-4\">We&#x27;d love to hear from you. Send your article idea, writing samples, or completed draft to:</p><p class=\"mt-6 text-xl font-medium text-neutral-900\">editor@tinysorted.com</p><p class=\"mt-6 text-neutral-600\">Please include:</p><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Your full name</li><li>Short author bio</li><li>Portfolio or website (optional)</li><li>Article title</li><li>Google Docs link or Word document</li></ul></section></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"   mt-40   border-t   border-neutral-200   bg-[#F7F6F3]   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   max-w-[1280px]   px-6   py-24   \"><div class=\"   grid   gap-16      md:grid-cols-2   lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]   \"><div><a href=\"/\"><h2 class=\"   text-2xl   font-light   uppercase   tracking-[0.32em]   text-neutral-900   transition   hover:opacity-70   \">Tinysorted</h2></a><p class=\"   mt-6   max-w-xl   text-neutral-600   leading-8   \">TinySorted helps people organize small spaces, simplify everyday living, and discover practical home solutions through thoughtfully researched articles and carefully selected product recommendations.</p><p class=\"   mt-6   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">Practical ideas for better living.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Explore</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/decluttering\">Decluttering</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/kitchen\">Kitchen</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Company</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/write-for-us\">Write For Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/advertise\">Advertise</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Legal</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/affiliate-disclosure\">Affiliate Disclosure</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Disclaimer</a></nav></div></div><div class=\"   mt-20   border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-10   \"><p class=\"   max-w-4xl   text-sm   leading-7   text-neutral-500   \">TinySorted participates in various affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this site, at no additional cost to you. Our recommendations are based on independent research and editorial judgment.</p></div><div class=\"   mt-12   flex   flex-col   gap-4      border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-8      md:flex-row   md:items-center   md:justify-between   \"><p class=\"   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> TinySorted. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"   flex   flex-wrap   gap-6      text-sm   text-neutral-500   \"><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/sitemap.xml\">Sitemap</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/rss.xml\">RSS</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Support</a></div></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14rn1owgzaaej.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\n2:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n3:I[79520,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[8821,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2tl5ylga63cnz.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n7:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n15:I[53348,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1-l_2hzb54z0b.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n:H